      "content": "i mean i know you say see a doctor but they're so hard to get an appointment with and it's gonna be expensive to go back to the clinic just for something small. the yellow stuff isn't a lot, just a tiny bit of fluid. do you really think i need a doctor if i just use an antiseptic cream and keep it covered? i really just want to handle it here if it's just a minor thing.",
