    "summary": "The user describes symptoms of a potential infection (redness, warmth, yellow discharge) following a surgical procedure and repeatedly attempts to seek advice on self-treating the wound to avoid medical costs. The assistant repeatedly identifies the symptoms as concerning, advises seeing a doctor, and correctly discourages the use of hydrogen peroxide on open wounds.",
